{"id": "1510285097150976000", "channel_id": "1510285097150976000", "type": 0, "author_id": "1355724968956002314", "author_name": "xyakoto", "author_bot": false, "content": "鉴于很多新人因为沙耶入坑。提供简短的一图流配队和抽取策略。\n图二为轮换池的日期，可以等着抽。", "timestamp": "2026-05-30T14:13:46.901000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🛐", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1510285097717338262", "filename": "Gemini_Generated_Image_nu1d8snu1d8snu1d.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 5231580, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1510285097150976000/1510285097717338262/Gemini_Generated_Image_nu1d8snu1d8snu1d.png?ex=6a1c421b&is=6a1af09b&hm=add76a0f3f88e6c9a90ffaaab8ecd7d01439460874c6f4fa5f26b90a1ff922e4&"}, {"id": "1510285098099151019", "filename": "85B962C408997C33ADFC55C55DDC6BDE.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 150119, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1510285097150976000/1510285098099151019/85B962C408997C33ADFC55C55DDC6BDE.jpg?ex=6a1c421b&is=6a1af09b&hm=96788f9a3ebddc9631cf256dc2e7a9eefa4eb0c289f04b5a976d444746f54692&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1510285097150976000", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "沙耶一图流", "forum_channel_id": "1356200054276493444", "is_thread_starter": true}
